Class EditTextErrorFixed

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.view.View
      • android.widget.TextView
        • android.widget.EditText
          • triageapp.activities.EditTextErrorFixed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Drawable.Callback, AccessibilityEventSource, KeyEvent.Callback, ViewTreeObserver.OnPreDrawListener

    public class EditTextErrorFixed
extends EditText
    EditText which addresses issues with the error icon (http://stackoverflow.com/q/13756978/832776) and also the error icon disappearing on pressing delete in an empty EditText in Android versions 4.2 and 4.2.1.
    Author:
    Oleg Vaskevich (http://stackoverflow.com/a/14175640/832776)
